{
  "title": "Sherwin Carlquist Publications Dataset",
  "description": "Comprehensive bibliographic metadata for 343 scientific publications by botanist Sherwin Carlquist (1930-2021), spanning 1956-2021. The dataset documents his contributions to plant systematics, wood anatomy, island biogeography, and evolutionary biology. Metadata follows Citation Style Language (CSL-JSON) and Dublin Core standards, with enrichment from CrossRef DOI database.",
